{"data":[{"id":561690193,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fc8b0d2185e311c5c6aa76865c9a7168","url_token":"flute60564","name":"flute60564","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-63653259a0b4e91187d8014f36177851_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-63653259a0b4e91187d8014f36177851_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/fc8b0d2185e311c5c6aa76865c9a7168","user_type":"people","headline":"延期狗/已毕业/非895毕业/年薪不到500k/房价不会崩/单反不会亡/求打脸","badge":[{"type":"identity","description":"教育学博士","topics":[]}],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":74,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561690193","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545989597,"updated_time":1545989597,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"comment_count":3,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e谢邀\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我真的是飘了，居然有人邀请我回答这种问题，我哪里回答过数学类的问题啊，关注问题好几天了，为什么要这时候邀请我啊~\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我不是数学系的，只系统的学过微积分、线性代数和数理统计这些简单的课程，数学分析和数论都没有正式的学过，教材对我这种垃圾土博来说看起来也很难，学起来一点都不愉快。做个简单的，不太合适的类比，任何一个数学系的研究生来讲，如果能证明低二、三个档次的猜想，发篇AMC，嗯，一路畅通到二级教授，安家费年薪配偶工作加上任何需求，基本就是一生无忧了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是吧，我大概知道题主这句话什么意思，可以简单从这个角度讲一下。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这么说吧，这个问题火也不是没有道理的，知乎大部分用户都在15到35之间，大都受过，或者即将受高等教育。这也造成了知乎用户心气儿高、学历高、收入高、牛皮吹的响等一系列现象。但是哥猜的能力和保送的需求二者严重不对等，任何人如果有能力证明哥德巴赫猜想，那就是在世界顶峰，入选全世界教材，成为世界典范的人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有这个能力的人，不会以“保送清北”为自己的奋斗目标。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主的需求翻译成大家的需求，大概是这么个意思：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e大学版：如果我GPA 4.0，雅思10，托福120，能申请黑龙江东方学院的研究生么？\u003cbr\u003e研究生版：如果我一年能发一篇Nature和Science，够资格到海南软件职业技术学院工作么？\u003cbr\u003e普通人版：如果我年入上千万，能买得起我们县城的别墅么？\u003cbr\u003e疯子版：如果我找到了让人长生不老的药，卖50块钱一颗会不会太贵了？\u003cbr\u003e（如果有以上两所学校的师生看到了，我是随机百度的学校，无恶意，见谅）\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"谢邀我真的是飘了，居然有人邀请我回答这种问题，我哪里回答过数学类的问题啊，关注问题好几天了，为什么要这时候邀请我啊~我不是数学系的，只系统的学过微积分、线性代数和数理统计这些简单的课程，数学分析和数论都没有正式的学过，教材对我这种垃圾土博…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=216\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Cco